author_ssm: Jasmine Soliman and Jonathan Burr for Akkasah Photography Archive, NYUAD
unittitle_ssm: Vers la Tunisie...Sur le "Kairouan" (A Trip to Tunisia on the Kairouan)
abstract_ssm: A travel album of a trip to Tunisia from Marseille on the ship "Kairouan" circa 1950s, containing 107 gelatin silver photographs. Places visited are: Tunis, Carthage, Sidi Bou Said, Nabeul, Hammamet, Monastie, Mahdia, Sousse,El Djem, Gabes, Sfax, Matmatas, Douiret, Djerba, Gafsa, Medenine and Kairouan. Creator unknown.
